msgstr "Status atual e planos futuros"

#. type: Plain text
#. mt: deepl
#: _posts/2025-07-15-quickjs4j.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"The extension is currently in **experimental status**, meaning APIs may evolve based on\n"
